Final 23 March 2023

Upstream (west) of causeway behind TGSHS – Brendan McIntyre group

8N - Backhousia myrtifolia – Grey myrtle – 17 cms

9N - Backhousia myrtifolia – Grey myrtle – 15 cms

10N - Glochidion ferdinandi – Cheese tree – multi 22, 10, 14, 9 cms

11N - Lophostemon suaveolens – Swamp box – 13 cms

12N - Streblus brunonianus – Whalebone tree – multi 17, 19 cms

13N - Elaeocarpus obovatus – Hard quandong – 59 cms

14N - Legnephora moorei – Round-leaved vine – 3 cms

15N - Aphanopetalum resinosum – Gum vine – 3 cms

26N - Waterhousea floribunda - Weeping lilly pilly – multi 31, 30, 22, 15, 27, 8, 37

cms

28N - Ficus sp. – multi 64, 64 cms

29N - Ficus sp. – multi 64, 29 cms
